		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=dethbringre&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Sup guys just started a new bard on tribunal... came over from bertoxx , have no idea about the strategies of a bard... ive been playing a warrior... could somebody just give me the lowdown on how to play a bard in a group setting as well as a solo scene... also could i get informed on how to twist songs and the use of instruments... thanks&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />gamer...<br><br>Dethbringre 31 rogue Mannoroth</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >7 Replies</td></tr></table>
